room_title: Escape room "Black Ops" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
review: We did the Black Ops task and it was very challenging, but loads of fun. Lisa was our guide and she gave us the perfect clues which challenged us to think analytically to get through the task. 10/10 would recommend going to Escape Chambers. Will feel very rewarded working your way through the challenges.
